Class Account

java.lang.Object
Account
Direct Known Subclasses:
Checking, Credit, Savings
public abstract class Account
extends java.lang.Object
Account class is a parent of all other classes such as Checking, Savings, and Credit. Methods are included in this class as well as getters and setters that will allow for the function of entire program.
Since:
September 29,2020
